{"service_name": "Risk Assessment & Management", "service_id": "5460528256253952", "company_name": "BMT Hi-Q Sigma Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     BMT Hi-Q Sigma Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Risk Assessment &amp; Management\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Our Risk Management services enable you to identify, assess and manage risks We use Association of Project Management\u2019s (APM) Project Risk &amp; Analysis Management (PRAM) Guide, Cabinet Office Management of Risk (M_o_R) and Institute of Risk Management (IRM) guidance and methodologies to deliver a complete understanding of threats and opportunities.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     5-step process aligned with APM PRAM Guide\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Comprehensive assessment of threats and opportunities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk workshops designed and run to explore threat scenarios\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Quantitative risk analysis using recognised risk analysis tools\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk management strategy to reduce likelihood of occurrence and/or impact\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Comprehensive risk response, risk mitigation and action plans\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk reporting mechanisms and dashboards developed appropriate to each project\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Qualified practitioners, experienced across a range of projects and domains\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Transfer of risk management skills and techniques\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Early and detailed warning of potential issues\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reduces your organisation\u2019s overall risk exposure\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides senior managers with risk-based view linked to business objectives\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Increases stakeholder confidence in achieving desired outcomes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     More accurate and efficient estimating and resource planning\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Builds a risk aware and improved risk management culture\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3598 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92598/5460528256253952-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92598/5460528256253952-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92598/5460528256253952-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </